hadiths[145]{hadithnumber,text}:
1638,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ibne-Adam key har amal (key sawab) mein izafa kiya jata hai, neki ka sawab das guna sey saat sau guna balke (us sey bhi ziyada) jitna Allah chahey milta hai. Allah Taala farmata hai : magar roza (is qanoon sey mustasna (alag) hai) kyonkey wo (khaalisatan) merey liye hota hai aur main hi uski jaza dunga. banda meri khatir apni khaahishat aur khana tarak karta hai. roze-daar key liye do khushiyan hain : eik khushi roza kholtey waqt (hasil hoti hai) aur eik khushi apney Rab sey mulaqat key waqt (hasil hogi). Allah key yahan roze-daar key munh ki boo kastoori ki mahak sey bhi ziyada umda hai."
1639,"Hazrat Mutrif bin Abdullah (Rahimahullah) jo qabila banu Aamir bin Sasaa sey they, un sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Usman bin Abul-Aas Saqafi (Raziallahu anhu) ney unhen pilaney key liye doodh talab farmaya. Mutrif (Rahimahullah) ney kaha : main rozey sey hun. Hazrat Usman Saqafi (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna , aap farma rahey they : roza jahannam sey bachaney wali dhaal hai jis tarah ladaai main tum mein sey kisi ki dhaal hoti hai."
1640,"Hazrat Sehal bin Saad (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jannat main eik darwaza hai jisey Rayyaan kaha jata hai. qiyamat key din aawaz di jaeygi, kaha jaeyga : rozey rakhney waley kahan hain? chunanche jo shakhs roza rakhney walon mein sey hoga wo us (darwazey) mein dakhil ho jaeyga. aur jo is mein dakhil hoga, usey kabhi piyas nahin lageygi."
1641,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs eman rakhtey huye aur sawab ki niyat sey Ramzan key rozey rakhey , uskey sabiqa (pichhle) gunah maaf ho jaeyngey."
1642,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab Ramzan ki pehli raat aati hai to shetanon aur sarkash jinon ko jakad diya jata hai. jahannam key darwazey band kar diye jatey hain, un mein sey koi darwaza khula nahin rehta aur jannat key darwazey khol diye jatey hain, un mein sey koi darwaza band nahin rehta. aur eik aelan karney wala manadi karta hai : aey neki key talab gaar, aagey badh aur aey burai key talabgar ruk ja. aur Allah Taala jahannam sey (baaz) logon ko azad karta hai. (Ramzan mein) har raat isi tarah hota hai."
1643,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah Taala har iftaar key waqt kuchh logon ko azad farmata hai. aur ye (Ramzan ki) har raat mein hota hai."
1644,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : Ramzan ka mahina shuru huwa to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tumharey paas ye mahina aa gaya hai, is main eik raat hai jo hazar mahiney sey afzal hai, jo us raat (ka sawab hasil kerney) sey mehroom raha, wo har bhalai sey mehroom raha. uskey khair sey wohi mehroom rehta hai jo waaqaee mehroom hai."
1645,"Hazrat Sila bin Zufr (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : hum log Hazrat Ammar (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein hazir they aur din wo tha jis mein shak kiya jata hai. aap ki khidmat main eik (pakaaee hui) bakri pesh ki gaee. baaz log (khaney sey ijtinab kartey (bachte) huye) eik taraf ho gaey. Hazrat Ammar (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : jisney is din roza rakha, usney Abul-Qaasim (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki nafarmani ki."
1646,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney chaand nazar aaney sey eik din pehley jaldi kartey huye roza rakhney sey mana farmaya."
1647,"Hazrat abu-Abdur-Rehman Qasim bin Abdur-Rehman bin Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke unhoney Hazrat Muawiya bin abu-Sufiyaan (Raziallahu anhuma) ko member par ye farmatey suna ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) maahe Ramzan (shuru honey) sey pehley member par farma diya kartey they : roza falan din hoga, aur hum (aadatan) is sey pehley roza rakhney waley hain. ab jo chahey pehley shuru kar ley , aur jo chahey baad mein (Ramzan shuru honey par roza rakhna) shuru karey."
1648,"Ummul-mominin Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Shoban ko Ramzan sey mila detey they."
1649,Hazrat Rabeea bin Ghaaz (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai ke unhoney Ummul-mominin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key rozon key barey mein sawal kiya to Ummul-mominin (Raziallahu anha) ney farmaya : aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) pura Shoban rozey rakhtey they yahan tak key usey Ramzan sey mila detey they.
1650,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Ramzan (shuru honey) sey eik do din pehley roza na rakho. siwaye us shakhs key jo pehley sey wo roza rakhta chala aa raha ho to us din bhi rakh ley."
1651,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab Shoban aadha ho jaey to Ramzan aa janey tak koi roza nahin."
1652,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : eik Erabi (dehati) (dehaati) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa aur arz kiya : mainey aaj raat chaand dekha hai. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kya to gawahi deta hai ke Allah key siwa koi mabood nahin aur Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Allah key Rasool hain? usney kaha : ji haan. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Bilal ! utho, logon mein aelan kar do ke kal roza rakhen. eik riwayat mein hai : Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ney aelan kar diya ke wo qiyam karen aur roza rakhen."
1653,"Hazrat Abu Umer Abdullah bin Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : mujhey merey chachaon ney hadees sunai, jo Ansari Sabab they, unhoney farmaya : hamein Shawwaal ka chaand (badal waghera ki wajeh sey) nazar na aaya to hamney subah ko roza rakh liya. din key aakhiri hissey main eik qafila aaya un logon ney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key paas gawahi di ke unhoney kal chaand dekha hai to Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney logon ko hukm diya ke roza chhod den aur agley din eid key liye (eid gaah ki taraf) niklen."
1654,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab tum chaand dekho to rozey rakho, aur jab chaand dekho to rozey chhod do. agar tum par badal chha jaey to uska andaza kar lo. Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anha) chaand sey eik din pehley roza rakhtey they."
1655,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab tum chaand dekho to rozey rakho aur jab (dobara) chaand dekho to rozey rakhna chhod do. agar tum par badal ho jaeyn to tees din rozey rakh lo."
1656,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mahiney ka kitna hissa guzar gaya hai? hamney kaha : baais (din guzar gaey hain), aur baqi aath din hain. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mahina itna hota hai aur mahina itna hota hai, aur mahina itna hota hai. aap ney teen baar ye alfaz farmaaey aur (teesri baar) eik ungli band farma li."
1657,"Hazrat Saad bin Abi Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mahina itna, itna aur itna hota hai.  aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney teesri baar key isharay sey untees ka ishara mukammal kiya."
1658,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hamney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key ehad Mubarak mein tees rozon ki nisbat untees rozey ziyada dafa rakhey."
1659,"Hazrat abu-Bakra (Nufai bin Haris Saqafi) (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : eid key do mahiney naqis nahin hotey, yani Ramzan aur Zul-hijja."
1660,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Eidul-Fitr us din hai jis din tum (Ramzan mukammal kar key) roza chhodtey ho, aur Eidul-Azhaa us din hai jis din tum qurbani kartey ho."
1661,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney safar mein (kabhi) roza rakha, aur (kabhi) chhod diya."
1662,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Hamza bin Amr Aslami (Raziallahu anhu) ney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey sawal kiya aur kaha : main (nafli) rozey rakha karta hun, kya safar mein bhi roza rakh liya karun? Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : agar to chahey to roza rakh ley, chahey to chhod dey."
1663,"Hazrat Abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey dekha ke hum log eik safar mein Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sath they aur us din shadeed garmi thi yahan tak key aadmi garmi ki shiddat sey bachney key liye apney sar par haath rakh leta tha. (us din qafiley key) logon mein kisi ka roza nahin tha siwaye Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aur Hazrat Abdullah bin Rawaha (Raziallahu anhu) key."
1664,Hazrat Kaab bin Aasim (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : safar mein roza rakhna neki nahin.
1665,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : safar mein roza rakhna neki nahin."
1666,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Auf (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : safar mein Ramzan ka roza rakhney wala aisey hi hai jaisey ghar mein hotey huye roza na rakhney wala. Abu-Is'haq ney farmaya : ye hadees kisi kaam ki nahin."
1667,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, ye Sahaba qabila banu Abdul-Ash'hal ki shaakh banu Abdullah bin Kaab sey hain. unhoney kaha : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key ghud sawar dastey ney hamarey qabiley par hamla kiya. main Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa to aap khana kha rahey they to aap ney farmaya : aa jao, khana kha lo. mainey kaha : mera roza hai. farmaya : beth jao ! main tumhen rozey ki baat bataun. Allah Taala ney musafir ko aadhi namaz maaf kar di hai, aur musafir, hamila aur doodh pilaney wali ko roza ya rozey maaf kar diye hain. Allah ki qism ! Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney ye dono lafz farmaae ya un mein sey eik lafz farmaya. mujhey apney aap par afsos hai ke main Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key khaney mein shareek na huwa."
1668,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney us hamila ko, jisey apni jaan ka khatra ho roza chhodney ki rukhsat (chhoot) di hai, aur doodh pilaney wali us aurat ko bhi (rukhsat (chhoot) di hai) jisey apney bachchey key barey mein (nuqsan pahunchney ka) khof ho."
1669,"Ummul-mominin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : merey zimmey Ramzan key rozey hotey they to main un ki qaza nahin deti thi yahan tak key Shoban aa jata."
1670,"Ummul-mominin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key yahan rehtey huye hamen haiz aata tha to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamein rozey ki qaza ka hukm detey they."
1671,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : eik aadmi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa aur bola, main tabah ho gaya. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : to kaisey tabah ho gaya? usney kaha : main Ramzan main apni biwi sey hum bistari kar betha hun. to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : eik insan (ghulam ya londi) azad karo. usney kaha : merey paas (ghulam kharidney key liye maal) nahin. aap ney farmaya : musalsal do maah rozey rakh lo. usney kaha : mujh mein iski taqat nahin. aap ney farmaya : saath (60) miskinon ko khana khila do. usney kaha : merey paas (itna maal bhi) nahin. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : beth jao. to wo beth gaya. isi beech mein aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein (khajuron ka) eik tokraa laya gaya, jisey araq kaha jata hai. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jao, ye sadqa kar do. usney kaha : Allah key Rasool ! qism hai us zaat ki, jisney aap ko haq dey kar mab-us farmaya (bheja), Madiney mein dono pathreeley ilaqon key darmiyan koi gharaanaa hum sey ziyada iska zarurat mand nahin. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jao aur ye apney ehal aur ayaal ko khila do. eik dusri sanad sey Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey marvi (riwayat hui) hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : is (rozey) ki jagah eik din ka roza rakh lena."
1672,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney baghair uzr key Ramzan ka eik bhi roza chhod diya, uskey badley zamaney bhar key rozey bhi kafi nahin hongey."
1673,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney rozey ki haalat mein bhool kar kuchh kha liya, usey chahiye ke apna roza pura karey, usey Allah ney khilaya aur pilaya hai."
1674,"Hazrat Asma binte Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key zamaney main eik abr-aalood (baadlon bhare) din mein hamney roza khol diya (ye samjhey ke suraj ghurub ho chuka hai) lekin phir (badal hat gaey aur) suraj nikal aaya. (Abu-Usaama (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain : ) mainey Hisham bin Urwa (Rahimahullah) sey kaha : kya unhen (rozey ki) qaza ka hukm diya gaya tha? unhoney kaha : ye to zaruri tha."
1675,"Hazrat Fazala bin Ubaid Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eik aisey din unkey paas tashrif laye jis din aap roza rakha kartey they. aap ney (pani ka) bartan talab farmaya aur pi liya. hamney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! ye to wo din hai jis din aap roza rakha kartey they. farmaya : haan, lekin mujhey qai aa gaee thi."
1676,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis ko khud-ba-khud qai aa jaey, is par qaza nahin, aur jo qazdan qai kerey. is par qaza zaruri hai."
1677,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : rozey daar key behtareen kaamon mein sey eik amal miswak bhi hai."
1678,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney rozey ki haalat mein surma lagaya."
1679,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : seengi laganey waley aur lagwaaney waley ney roza khol diya."
1680,"Hazrat Soban (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko ye farmatey suna hai : seengi laganey waley aur lagwaaney waley ney roza khol diya."
1681,Hazrat Shaddad bin Aus (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke wo maqame Baqee mein Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sath chaley ja rahey they ke aap eik aadmi key paas sey guzrey jo seengi lagwaa raha tha. us waqt Ramzan ki atthaara raaten guzar chuki thin to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : seengi laganey waley aur lagwaaney waley ney roza khol diya.
1682,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney roza rakh kar ehraam ki haalat mein seengi lagwaai."
1683,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) maahe Ramzan mein (rozey ki haalat mein) bosa ley letey they."
1684,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) rozey ki haalat mein bosa ley letey they. aur tum mein sey kisey apni khahish par itna qabu ho sakta hai, jitna Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko apni khahish par qabu hasil tha?"
1685,Ummul-mominin Hazrat Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) rozey ki haalat mein bosa ley letey they.
1686,"Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki azad karda londi Hazrat Memuna binte sa'ad (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey sawal kiya gaya ke agar mard apni biwi ka bosa ley ley jabke un dono ka roza ho (to kya hukm hai)? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : un dono ney roza khol diya."
1687,Hazrat Ibrahim Nakhai (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Aswad aur Hazrat Masruq (Rahimahullah) Ummul-mominin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ki khidmat mein hazir huye aur kaha : kya Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) rozey ki haalat mein mubashrat kartey they? Ummul-mominin (Raziallahu anha) ney farmaya : aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aisey kar liya kartey they lekin aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko apni khahish par tum sey ziyada qabu hasil tha.
1688,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : boodhey rozey daar ko biwi sey mubashrat (muaaniqa (gale milna) waghera) ki ijazat hai, aur jo unkey liye makrooh hai."
1689,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney jhoot aur behuda baaton aur behuda kaamon sey ijtinab na kiya (na bachaa), Allah ko koi zarurat nahin ke wo shakhs khana peena tarak kar dey."
1690,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : baaz rozey daaron ko rozey sey bhook key siwa kuchh nahin milta aur baaz qiyam karney walon ko qiyam sey bedaari key siwa kuchh nahin milta."
1691,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab tum mein sey kisi ka din ko roza ho to wo fohsh goi (gandi baate) na karey aur naarawaa (na-jaayaz) harkat na karey , agar koi us sey badtameezi karey to keh dey mein rozey daar aadmi hun."
1692,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : sehri khaya karo kyonkey sehri mein barkat hai."
1693,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : sehri key khaney key sath din key rozey key liye madad hasil karo, aur qailule key zariey sey qiyamul-lail (Namaze-Tahajjud) key liye madad hasil karo."
1694,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Hazrat Zaid bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : hamney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sath sehri khai , phir uth kar namaz ki taraf chaley. (Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : ) mainey kaha : un dono kamon key darmiyan kitna waqfa tha? Hazrat Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : pachas aayaton ki tilawat jitna."
1695,"Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sath sehri khai jabke din nikal aaya tha lekin suraj tulu nahin huwa tha. Imam Abu-Is'haq (Rahimahullah) ney kaha : Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees mansookh hai aur kuchh bhi nahin."
1696,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum mein sey kisi ko Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ki Azan sehri khaney sey rukaawat na ho, wo to isliye Azan deta hai ke tum mein sey jo so raha hai wo jaag jaey, aur jo qiyam kar raha hai wo (namaze Fajr ki tayyari ki taraf) lot jaey. aur Fajr ye nahin ke (roshni) is tarah (oopper ko buland) ho jaey, balke is tarah hai, yani aasman key ufaq par chorai key rukh phel jaey."
1697,"Hazrat Sehal bin Saad (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : log us waqt tak bhalai par rahengey jab tak roza jaldi kholtey rahengey."
1698,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : log us waqt tak bhalai par rahengey jab tak roza jaldi kholtey rahengey. roza jaldi khola karo kyonkey Yahudi der kartey hain."
1699,"Hazrat Salman bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab koi roza kholey to usey chahiye ke khushk khajoor sey roza kholey, agar (khajoor) na miley to pani sey roza khol ley, kyonkey wo pak karney wala hai."
1700,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) ney Ummul-mominin Hazrat Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat kartey huye farmaya ke Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs raat sey rozey ka pukhta irada na karey , uska koi roza nahin."
1701,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) merey paas tashrif latey aur farmatey : kya aap logon key paas koi (khaney ki) chiz hai? hum kehtey : nahin, to farmatey : mera roza hai. phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) roza rakhey rehtey. phir hamein hadiye key tor par koi chiz mil jati to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) roza chhod detey. Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) baaz oqaat roza rakhtey aur (baaz oqaat) khol detey. (Hazrat Mujahid (Rahimahullah) ney farmaya : ) mainey kaha : ye kaisey ho sakta hai? Ummul-mominin (Raziallahu anha) ney farmaya : uski misal aisey hai jaisey koi shakhs sadqa (deney key liye kuch raqam) nikalta hai. phir (is mein sey) kuchh (kisi mustahiq ko) dey deta hai aur kuchh apney paas rakh leta hai."
1702,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Kaba ke Rab ki qism ! ye baat main (apni taraf sey) nahin kehta, Hazrat Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney ye farmaya hai : jisey janabat (hambistari ke bad napaki) ki haalat mein subah ho jaey, wo roza chhod dey."
1703,"Ummul-mominin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko raat key waqt janabat (hambistari ke bad napaki) ki haalat pesh aa jati thi, (subah honey par) Hazrat Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) hazir ho kar namaz ka waqt ho janey ki ittilaa detey to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) uth kar ghusl farma letey (ghusl sey farigh honey par) main aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sar Mubarak sey pani tapakta dekhti, phir aap tashrif ley jatey aur main Fajr ki namaz mein aap ki (tilawat ki) aawaz sunti. (sanad key eik Raavi) Mutrif (Rahimahullah) ney kaha : mainey Imam Aamir Shaabey (Rahimahullah) sey kaha : kya Ramzan mein (Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) is tarah kartey they)?  unhoney farmaya : Ramzan aur ghair Ramzan barabar hain."
1704,"Hazrat Nafey (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : mainey Ummul-mominin Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) sey daryaft kiya ke agar aadmi ko janabat (hambistari ke bad napaki) ki haalat mein subah ho jaey aur wo roza rakhna chahta ho (to kya hukm hai)? Ummul-mominin (Raziallahu anha) ney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko bhi is haal mein subah ho jati thi ke aap ko khuwab ki wajeh sey nahin, balke mubashrat (hambistari) ki wajeh sey ghusl ki hajat hoti thi. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ghusl kar key apna roza mukammal farma letey they."
1705,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Shikhkhir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney hamesha rozey rakhey, usney na roza rakha, na iftaar kiya."
1706,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney hamesha roza rakha, usney roza rakha hi nahin."
1707,"Hazrat Minhaal (Raziallahu anhu) Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey riwayat kartey hain ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) beez ke din key rozey rakhney ka hukm detey they, yani tera, chaudah aur pandarah taareekh ko aur farmatey they : ye hamesha key rozon ki tarah hai, ya hamesha key rozon ki si kaifiyat hai.  Imam Ibne-Maja (Rahimahullah) ney yehi riwayat Is-haq bin Mansoor key wastey sey Qatada bin Milhaan key tareeq sey bhi riwayat ki hai. Imam Ibne-Maja (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain : is riwayat mein Shoba ney ghalati ki aur Hamaam ney sahih riwayat bayan ki (Shoba ney isey Abdul-Malik bin Minhaal sey riwayat kiya hai to darasal Abdul-Malik bin Qatada bin Milhaan sey marvi (riwayat hui) hai)."
1708,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney har mahiney mein teen rozey rakhey to yehi hamesha key rozey hain. Allah Taala ney apni kitab mein iski taeed nazil farma di : (مَنْ جَاءَ بِالْحَسَنَةِ فَلَهُ عَشْرُ أَمْثَالِهَا),''jo shakhs neki ley kar hazir huwa, uskey liye uska das guna (sawab) hai.'' chunanche eik din (key rozey) sey das din ka sawab milta hai."
1709,"Hazrat Muaza Adwiya (Rahimahullah) Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat karti hain, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) har mahiney mein teen rozey rakhtey they, (Hazrat Muaza Adwiya (Rahimahullah) ney bayan kiya) mainey kaha : mahiney key kis hissey mein? unhoney kaha : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) is baat ki parwah nahin kartey they ke kon sey hissey mein (rozey rakhey) hain."
1710,"Hazrat Abu-Salma (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : mainey Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key rozon key barey mein sawal kiya to Ummul-mominin (Raziallahu anha) ney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) rozey rakhtey they yahan tak key hum kehtey ke ab to aap rozey hi rakhtey jaeyngey. aur rozey chhodtey to hum kehtey ke ab to aap ney rozey chhod hi diye hain. mainey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko kabhi Shoban sey ziyada kisi mahiney mein rozey rakhtey nahin dekha. aap (taqreeban) pura Shoban hi rozey rakh letey they. aap chand din key siwa maahe Shoban key (sarey) rozey rakh letey they."
1711,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) (musalsal) rozey rakhtey they yahan tak key hum kehtey : aap iftaar nahin kerengey. aur iftaar kartey yahan tak key hum kehtey : aap rozey nahin rakhengey. aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab sey Madina tashrif laye, aap ney Ramzan key siwa kabhi musalsal eik mahine rozey nahin rakhey."
1712,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr bin Aas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah ko sab sey ziyada mehbub roza Dawud (Alaihissalam) wala roza hai. aap eik din roza rakhtey they aur eik din chhodtey they. aur Allah ko sab sey ziyada jo namaz pasand hai wo Dawud (Alaihissalam) ki namaz hai. aap aadhi raat tak sotey aur tihai raat mein namaz padhtey aur raat ka chhata hissa so rehtey."
1713,"Hazrat Abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : aey Allah key Rasool ! jo shakhs do din rozey rakhey aur eik din chhod dey to uska ye mamool kaisa hai? Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kya koi shakhs iski taqat rakhta hai? unhoney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! jo shakhs eik din roza rakhey aur eik din chhodey uska ye mamool kaisa hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ye Dawud (Alaihissalam) ka roza hai.  unhoney kaha : jo shakhs eik din roza rakhey aur do din chhodey uska ye mamool kaisa hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mera ji chahta hai ke main ye mamool ikhtiyar kar sakoon."
1714,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna aap farma rahey they : Hazrat Nuh (Alaihissalam) Eidul-Fitr ka din aur Eidul-Azhaa ka din chhod kar hamesha rozey rakhtey they."
1715,"Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key azad karda ghulam Hazrat Soban (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis shakhs ney Eidul-Fitr key baad chhe rozey rakhey, uskey purey saal key rozey ho gaey. (مَنْ جَاءَ بِالْحَسَنَةِ فَلَهُ عَشْرُ أَمْثَالِهَا),''jo shakhs neki karey, uskey liye uska das guna sawab hai."""
1716,"Hazrat Abu-Ayyub (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis shakhs ney Ramzan key rozey rakhey, phir uskey baad Shawwaal mein chhe rozey bhi rakh liye to usney goya zamaney bhar rozey rakhey."
1717,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs Allah ki raah main eik din roza rakhega, Allah Taala us din ki wajeh sey uskey chehrey sey jahannam ko sattar saal key fasley tak door kar dega."
1718,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs Allah ki raah main eik din roza rakhega, Allah Taala uskey chehrey ko jahannam sey sattar saal key fasley tak door kar dega."
1719,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Mina key din khaney peeney key din hain."
1720,"Hazrat Bishr bin Saheem (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney tashreeq ke din mein khutba irshad farmaya, (is khutbey key doran mein) aap ney farmaya : jannat mein sirf musalman jaan hi dakhil hogi. aur ye din khaney peeney key din hain."
1721,Hazrat Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Eidul-Fitr aur Eidul-Azhaa key din roza rakhney sey mana farmaya.
1722,"Hazrat Abu-Ubaid (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : main Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) key sath Eid mein hazir tha. Ameerul-Mominin (Raziallahu anhu) ney khutbey sey pehley namaz shuru ki aur (namaz key baad khutba detey huye) farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney in do dino ka roza rakhney sey mana farmaya hai, yani Eidul-Fitr key din aur Eidul-Azhaa key din. Eidul-Fitr ka din to tumhara rozon sey farigh honey ka din hai aur Eidul-Azhaa key din tum apni qurbaaniyon ka gosht khatey ho."
1723,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Jumey key din ka roza rakhney sey mana farmaya hai, siwaye us surat key ke us sey eik din pehley ya eik din baad bhi roza rakh liya jaey."
1724,"Hazrat Muhammad bin Ibaad bin Jaafar (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai ke unhoney kaha : main Baitullah ka tawaf kar raha tha, is doran mein mainey Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) sey sawal kiya : kya Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Jumey ka roza rakhney sey mana farmaya hai? unhoney farmaya : haan, qism hai is ghar key Rab ki !"
1725,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko Jumey ka roza kam hi chhodtey dekha hai."
1726,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Basar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : haftey key din ka roza na rakho, siwaye is rozey key jo tum par farz ho. agar kisi ko mehaz angoor ki shaakh ya kisi darkht ki chhaal hi miley to usi ko choos ley. Imam Ibne-Maja (Rahimahullah) ney farmaya : ye riwayat hamein Humaid bin Musada ney Sufiyan bin Habib sey, unhoney Soor bin Yazeed sey unhoney Khalid bin Maadaan sey, unhoney Abdullah bin Basar sey un ki hamsheera (bahan) key wastey sey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey mazkura hadees ki tarah bayan ki."
1727,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : koi din aisey nahin jin mein kiya huwa amal Allah ko un dino (mein kiye huye usi amal) sey ziyada mehbub ho.  yani Zul-hijja key pehley das dino mein. Sahaba Raziallahu anhum ney arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! Allah ki raah mein jihad bhi nahin? farmaya : Allah ki raah mein jihad bhi nahin ! magar jo shakhs apni jaan aur apna maal ley kar (jihad mein) nikla, phir kuchh bhi ley kar wapis na aaya."
1728,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : duniya key dino mein koi din aisa nahin jis mein ibadat karna Allah ko un das dino ki ibadat sey ziyada mehbub ho. un main eik din ka roza saal bhar key rozon key barabar hai. aur un ki eik eik raat shabbe-qadr key barabar hai."
1729,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko das dino mein kabhi rozey rakhtey nahin dekha."
1730,"Hazrat Abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Arfe key din key rozey ki wajeh sey main Allah sey ummid rakhta hun ke wo is sey pehley saal bhar key aur iskey baad key saal bhar key gunah maaf farma dega."
1731,"Hazrat Qatada bin Noman (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna , aap farma rahey they : jis shakhs ney Arfa key din roza rakha, uskey eik saal aagey aur eik saal peechhey key gunah maaf ho jaeyngey."
1732,"Hazrat Ikrima (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : main Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) key ghar mein un ki khidmat mein hazir huwa. mainey un sey Arafat key maidan mein Arfa key din ka roza rakhney key barey mein sawal kiya to Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Arafat mein Arfa key din ka roza rakhney sey mana farmaya hai."
1733,"Ummul-mominin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Aashoora (das mohrram) key din roza rakhtey they, aur us din roza rakhney ka hukm detey they."
1734,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Madina Munawra tashrif laye to yahudiyon ko (Aashoora ka) roza rakhtey paya. aap ney farmaya : ye kya hai? unhoney kaha : ye wo din hai jis mein Allah ney Musa (Alaihissalam) ko najat di aur Firon ko gharq kiya to Musa (Alaihissalam) ney (is nemat key) shukar key taur par roza rakha (isliye hum bhi roza rakhtey hain). to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Musa (Alaihissalam) par hamara haq tum sey ziyada hai. chunanche aap ney us din ka roza rakha aur roza rakhney ka hukm diya."
1735,"Hazrat Muhammad bin Saifi Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Aashoora key din hamein farmaya : kya tum mein sey kisi ney aaj khana khaya hai? hamney kaha : hum mein sey baaz ney khana khaya hai, baaz ney nahin khaya. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : din key baqi hissey ka roza pura karo, jisney khana khaya hai, (wo bhi baqi din ka roza rakhey) aur jisney nahin khaya, (wo bhi roza rakh ley) aur urooz-walon ko bhi kehla bhejo ke wo din key baqi hissey ka roza pura karen. hadees ke raawi bayan kartey hain ke, ""urooz-walon"" sey aap ki murad Madina key Aas paas key log they."
1736,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : agar main agley saal tak zinda raha to nau (9) taareekh ka roza zarur rakhunga. Abu-Ali ney kaha ke Ahmed bin Yunus ney ibne-Abi Zi'ib sey ye riwayat bayan ki to ye izafa bhi bayan kiya : (ye aap ney) is khatrey key peshe-nazar (farmaya) ke Aashoorey ka roza chhoot na jaey."
1737,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key paas Aashoora key din ka zikr huwa to aap ney farmaya : zamanae-jahiliyat key log us din roza rakha kartey they, chunanche ab jo shakhs uska roza rakhna chahta hai rakh ley aur jo shakhs roza nahin rakhna chahta , chhod dey."
1738,"Hazrat Abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Aashoora key din key rozey sey, main Allah sey is qadr sawab ki ummid rakhta hun ke is sey pehley eik saal key gunah maaf farma dega."
1739,Hazrat Rabeea bin Ghaaz (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai ke unhoney Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key rozon key mutalliq daryaft kiya to Ummul-mominin (Raziallahu anha) ney farmaya : aap Somwar aur Jumerat key rozey ka ehtimam farmatey they.
1740,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Somwar (peer) aur Jumerat ko roza rakha kartey they. arz kiya gaya : aey Allah key Rasool ! aap Somwar aur Jumerat ka roza rakhtey hain (iski kya wajeh hai)? farmaya : Somwar aur Jumerat ko Allah Taala har musalman ki maghfirat farma deta hai magar wo do aadmi jo aapas mein qata' talluq kiye huye hon. Allah Taala farmata hai : unhen chhod do yahan tak key suleh kar lein.
1741,"Hazrat Abu Mujeeba Baahli (Rahimahullah) apney walid ya chacha (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat kartey hain, unhoney farmaya : main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa aur arz kiya : aey Allah key Nabi ! main wohi shakhs hun jo pichhley saal aap ki khidmat mein hazir huwa tha. aap ney farmaya : kya wajeh hai ke main tumharey jism ko kamzor dekhta hun? mainey kaha : Allah key Rasool ! mainey kabhi din key waqt khana nahin khaya (hamesha roze rakhta hun) sirf raat ko khana khata hun. aap ney farmaya : tujhey kis ney apni jaan ko azab mein dalney ka hukm diya hai? mainey arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! main taqat rakhta hun. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : sabr key mahiney (Ramzan) key rozey rakh aur iskey baad eik din roza rakh ley. mainey kaha : Allah key Rasool ! main ziyada taqat rakhta hun. aap ney farmaya : maahe-sabr key rozey rakh aur uskey baad do rozey (nafli) rakh ley. mainey kaha : main ziyada taqat rakhta hun. aap ney farmaya : maahe-sabr key rozey rakh aur uskey baad do rozey (nafli) rakh ley. mainey kaha : main ziyada taqat rakhta hun . aap ney farmaya : maahe-sabr key rozey rakh aur uskey baad teen din (aur rozey rakh ley) aur hurmat waley mahinon mein rozey rakh."
1742,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : eik aadmi ney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar kaha : maahe Ramzan key baad kon sey rozey afzal hain? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah key us mahiney key, jisey tum log mohrram kehtey ho."
1743,Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Rajab mein rozey rakhney sey mana farmaya.
1744,Muhammad bin Ibrahim Rahimahullah sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Usama bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhuma) hurmat waley mahinon key rozey rakhtey they. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney unhen farmaya : Shawwaal key mahiney key rozey rakho. chunanche unhoney hurmat waley mahinon key rozey chhod diye aur wafat tak shawwaal mein rozey rakhtey rahey.
1745,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : har chiz ki zakat hoti hai, aur jism ki zakat roza hai. eik riwayat key Raavi Mohariz ney ye izafa bayan kiya hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : roza aadha sabr hai."
1746,"Hazrat Zaid bin Khalid Juhni (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney rozey daar ka roza iftaar karaya, usey un (rozey daaron) key barabar sawab milega lekin unkey sawab mein kuch kami nahin hogi."
1747,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Zuber (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Hazrat Saad bin Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) key yahan roza iftaar kiya to farmaya : (أَفْطَرَ عِنْدَكُمُ الصَّائِمُونَ وَأَكَلَ طَعَامَكُمُ الأَبْرَارُ وَصَلَّتْ عَلَيْكُمُ الْمَلاَئِكَةُ), ''tumharey yahaan roze-daar rozey iftaar kartey rahen, tumhara khana nek log khaaeyn, aur farishtey tumharey liye rehmat ki duayen karen.''"
1748,"Hazrat Umme Imaara (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamarey yahan tashrif laye to hamney aap ki khidmat mein khana pesh kiya, aap key paas mojud afrad mein sey koi sahab rozey sey they to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : rozey daar key paas jab khana khaya jata hai to farishtey uskey haq mein dua kartey hain."
1749,Hazrat Suleman (Alaihissalam) bin Barida apney walid Hazrat Barida bin Haseeb Aslami (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat kartey hain ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Hazrat Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) sey farmaya : Bilal ! khana kha lo. unhoney kaha : mera to roza hai. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : hum log apna rizq kha rahey hain aur Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ka bacha huwa rizq jannat mein (mehfooz) hai. Bilal ! kya tumhen malum hai ke rozey daar key paas jab tak khana khaya jata rahey uski haddiyan tasbih padhti rehti hain aur farishtey uskey liye duaaey maghfirat kartey rehtey hain?
1750,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab tum mein sey kisi ko khaney ki dawat di jaey aur wo rozey sey ho to usey chahiye ke keh dey : main rozey sey hun."
1751,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisey khaney ki dawat di jaey aur wo rozey sey ho to usey chahiye ke dawat qubul kar ley , phir chahey khana khaye, chahey na khaye."
1752,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : teen aadmiyon ki dua radd nahin hoti : insaf karney wala hukmran, aur iftaar karney tak roze-daar, aur mazloom ki dua. qiyamat key din Allah Taala usey baadal key ooper uthaeyga, uskey liye aasman key darwazey khol diye jatey hain aur Allah Taala farmata hai : meri izzat ki qism ! main zarur teri madad karunga, chahey kuchh der baad hi karun."
1753,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : rozey daar key liye roza kholtey waqt eik dua aisi hoti hai jo radd nahin hoti. Abdullah bin Abi Muleka (Rahimahullah) bayan kartey hain ke mainey Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhuma) ko roza iftaar kartey waqt yun kehtey suna : (اللَّهُمَّ إِنِّى أَسْأَلُكَ بِرَحْمَتِكَ الَّتِى وَسِعَتْ كُلَّ شَىْءٍ أَنْ تَغْفِرَلِى), ''aey Allah ! main tujh sey teri us rehmat key wastey sey sawal karta hun jisney har chiz ko gher rakha hai ke to meri maghfirat farma dey.''"
1754,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Eidul-Fitr key din us waqt tak (eid ki namaz key liye) nahin nikaltey they jab tak chand khajuren na kha letey."
1755,Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Eidul-Fitr key din nikalney sey pehley Sahaba kiram ko sadqae fitr mein sey kuchh khila letey they.
1756,Hazrat Barida bin Haseeb Aslami (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Eidul-Fitr key din kuchh khaye baghair (Eid key liye) nahin nikaltey they aur qurbani key din (eid ki namaz sey) wapsi tak nahin khatey they.
1757,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs is haal mein faut ho jaey ke uskey zimmey maahe Ramzan key rozey hon to uski taraf sey har din (key rozey) ki jagah eik miskeen ko khana khila diya jaaey."
1758,Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke eik khatoon ney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar arz kiya : ya Rasoolullah ! meri hamsheera (bahan) faut ho gaee hai aur uskey zimmey musalsal do maah key rozey they. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : bhala agar teri behan par qarz hota to kya to usey ada karti? usney kaha : ji haan (zarur ada karti). aap ney farmaya : phir Allah ka haq (adaegi ka) ziyada mustahiq hai.
1759,Hazrat Barida bin Haseeb (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke unhoney farmaya : eik khatoon ney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! meri walida faut ho gaee aur unkey zimmey rozey they. kya main un ki taraf sey rozey rakhun? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : haan.
1760,"Hazrat Atiya bin Sufiyan bin Abdullah bin Rabeea (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hamara jo wafad banu-Saqif key Islam laney ki khabar ley kar Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa tha, unhoney mujhey bataya ke wo log maahe Ramzan mein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huye they. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney unkey liye masjid mein khema lagwaa diya. jab unhoney Islam qubul kar liya to unhoney maahe Ramzan key baqi dinon key rozey rakhey."
1761,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aurat apney khawind ki mojudgi mein uski ijazat key baghair maahe Ramzan key ilawa kisi din ka roza na rakhey."
1762,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney aurton ko apney khaawindon ki ijazat key baghair roza rakhney sey mana farmaya hai."
1763,"Ummul-mominin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab koi shakhs kuchh logon ka mehman ho to un ki ijazat key baghair roza na rakhey."
1764,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : khaney wala shukar-guzar sabr karney waley rozey-daar key darjey mein hai."
1765,"Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key Sahaba Hazrat Sanan bin Sannah Aslami (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : khaney waley shukar-guzar key liye sabr karney waley roza-daar jitna sawab hai."
1766,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hamney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sath Ramzan key darmiyani ashrey ka aetikaf kiya, phir aap ney farmaya : mujhey shabbe-qadr dikhai gaee thi, phir bhula di gaee. isey aakhiri dahaai ki taaq raaton mein talash karo."
1767,"Ummul-mominin Hazrat Aaisha Siddiqa (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aakhiri das dino mein itni mehnat kartey they, jitni aur dino mein nahin kartey they."
1768,"Ummul-mominin Hazrat Aaisha Siddiqa (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : jab aakhiri ushra shuru hota to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) raaton ko jaagtey, kamar kas letey aur ghar walon ko bhi bedaar kartey."
1769,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) har saal das din ka aetikaf kartey they, jab wo saal aaya jis mein aap ki wafat hui to aap ney bees din aetikaf kiya. aur aap par har saal eik baar Quran pesh kiya jata tha, jis saal Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki wafat hui, us saal aap ko do baar Quran ka daur karaya gaya."
1770,"Hazrat Ubai-bin Kaab (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Ramzan key aakhiri ashrey ka aetikaf kiya kartey they. eik saal aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) (aakhiri ashrey key doran mein) safar mein they to jab aglaa saal aaya , aap ney bees din aetikaf kiya."
1771,"Ummul-mominin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab aetikaf karna chahtey they to subah ki namaz padh kar us jagah dakhil hotey jahan aap ka aetikaf karney ka irada hota. (eik baar) aap ney Ramzan key aakhiri ashrey ka aetikaf karney ka irada farmaya. aap ney hukm diya to aap key liye khema laga diya gaya, Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ney bhi eik khema laganey ka hukm diya to unkey liye bhi laga diya gaya. Hazrat Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ney bhi eik khema laganey ka hukm diya to unkey liye bhi laga diya gaya. jab Hazrat Zenab (Raziallahu anha) ney un dono key khemey dekhey to unhoney bhi eik khema laganey ka hukm diya aur unkey liye bhi khema laga diya gaya . Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney jab ye chiz dekhi to farmaya : kya tum neki ka irada rakhti ho? chunanche Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Ramzan mein aetikaf nahin farmaya, aur shawwaal mein das din aetikaf kar liya."
1772,"Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke unhoney qubule Islam sey pehley eik raat key aetikaf ki nazar maana thi (jo Islam laney tak puri na kar sakey they), chunanche unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey masla daryaft kiya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney unhen aetikaf karney ka hukm diya."
1773,Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Ramzan key aakhiri das din aetikaf kiya kartey they. Hazrat Nafey (Rahimahullah) ney farmaya : Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) ney mujhey wo jagah dikhai thi jahan Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aetikaf kiya kartey they.
1774,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab aetikaf kartey to sutoone-tauba key qarib aap ka bistar bichha diya jata, ya aap ki chaar pai wahan bichha di jati."
1775,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney eik Turki mehraab mein aetikaf farmaya jis key darwazey par chataai ka eik tukda tha. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney haath sey chataai pakdi aur usey hata kar mehraab main eik taraf kar diya, phir apna sar (khemey sey) bahar nikal kar logon sey baat ki."
1776,"Ummul-mominin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main hajat key liye ghar mein dakhil hoti aur wahan koi bimar hota to main chaltey chaltey hi uski khairiyat poochh leti thi. unhoney farmaya : jab log aetikaf mein hotey they to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ghar mein dakhil nahin hotey they magar qazaey-hajat (peshaab pakhaana karne ke) key liye."
1777,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aetikaf wala janaazey key sath ja sakta hai aur bimar ki bimar pursi kar sakta hai."
1778,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aetikaf bethey hotey to apna sar merey qarib kar detey, main aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka sar Mubarak dho kar kanghi kar deti, main apney hujrey mein hoti thi aur dinon sey hoti thi aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) masjid mein hotey they."
1779,"Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki zauja mohtarma (biwi) Hazrat Safiya binte Huyee (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke wo Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey mulaqat key liye masjid mein tashrif ley gaeen jabke aap Ramzanul-Mubarak key aakhiri ashrey mein masjid mein aetikaaf mein they. wo Isha key waqt kuchh der Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey baat cheet karti rahin phir uth kar wapis chal den, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) unhen (masjid key darwazey tak) chhodney key liye unkey sath hi uth khadey huye. Hazrat Safeeya (Raziallahu anhu) jab masjid key us darwazey tak pahunchein jo Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki zauja mohtarma (biwi) Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) key hujrey key qarib tha to paas sey do Ansari guzrey. unhoney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko salam arz kiya aur chal diye. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney unhen farmaya : thehro, ye Safiya binte huyee (Raziallahu anha) hain.  unhoney kaha : Subhan Allah ! aey Allah key Rasool ! (hum aap par kis tarah shak kar saktey hain)? unhoney (Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki) is baat ko shiddat sey mehsus kiya. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : shetan insan mein khoon ki tarah phirta hai. mujhey khatra mehsus huwa tha ke wo tumharey dil mein koi (na munasib) baat na dal dey."
1780,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sath aap ki eik zauja mohtarma (biwi) ney aetikaf kiya. unhen surkh aur zard rang (ka istihaaza) aata tha. baaz oqaat wo apney nichey chaudaa bartan rakh liya karti thin."
1781,Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney aetikaf karney waley key barey mein farmaya : wo gunahon ko rok deta hai. aur uskey liye sari nekiyan anjam deney waley ki tarah nekiyan jari ki jati hain.
1782,"Hazrat abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney Allah sey sawab hasil karney ki niyat sey Eidain ki dono raaton mein qiyam kiya, uska dil nahin mareyga, jis din (logon key) dil mar jaeyngey."
